    {d:'hard',q:'The three aspects of designing a PR system are:', opts:['Input, Processing, Output','Data acquisition, Representation, Decision-making','Training, Testing, Deployment','Collection, Storage, Retrieval'], ans:1, exp:'The three main aspects are: Data acquisition & pre-processing, Data representation, and Determining the decision-making mechanism.'}
